snippet.title: Prince William Says His Kids Get Into ‘A Massive Fight’ Every Morning
snippet.description:
Prince William appeared on a special holiday episode of “Time To Walk" by Apple Fitness, where he admitted his kids get into a "massive fight" every morning over music. Plus, the Duke of Cambridge reveals the Tina Turner hit that brings back fond memories of his mother Princess Diana. Morgan Hoffman and Sangita Patel react on ET Canada Live.
#PrinceWilliam #KateMiddleton #PrincessDiana
